<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Autofs on 魔都水滴</title><link>https://blog.margrop.net/tag/autofs/</link><description>Recent content in Autofs on 魔都水滴</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 17 Feb 2021 21:15:19 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.margrop.net/tag/autofs/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Centos 7.4 NFS自动挂载</title><link>https://blog.margrop.net/post/centos-nfs-mount-autofs/</link><pubDate>Wed, 17 Feb 2021 21:15:19 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://blog.margrop.net/post/centos-nfs-mount-autofs/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="触发式自动挂载"&gt;触发式自动挂载&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;用户登录时自动挂载NFS共享目录&lt;code&gt;/home/share&lt;/code&gt;到本机&lt;code&gt;/mnt/share&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;yum install -y autofs
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;vi /etc/auto.master
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;/mnt /etc/auto.conf（这个配置文件本身就没有要自己创建）
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;vi /etc/auto.conf
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;share 192.168.1.22:/etc/letsencrypt/live/margrop.net-0001/（nfs服务器上共享文件）
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;service autofs restart 
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>